{
  "texts": [
    "We had two extra participants due to technical issues with Prolific.",
    "In accordance with our registered criteria, we excluded one participant for failing attention checks and another participant for providing bogus ratings with no variation across 50 trials.",
    "Our final sample included 671 participants (288 female, 376 male, 7 no gender or non-binary; age: M = 40.83 years, SD =12.89).",
    "Preparing vignettes.",
    "We prepared a set of 18 short textual descriptions of negative social situations experienced in everyday life (see Supplemental Information)."
  ]
}